&lt;p&gt;In the 2nd episode we discussed tips about how to pick an opensource project itself, not to be overwhelmed and also learn about opensource licenses.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We had Kavya Jaiswal and Pragati Verma join us and tell us about their opensource adventures.&lt;/p&gt;
